---
/**
 * TVA framework visual for /methodology/.
 *
 * Two layers:
 * 1. The TVA structure: Trigger → Value → Asset (with examples)
 * 2. The STA gate: scoring rubric with decision flow (≥7 send / <7 regen / 3 fails skip)
 */
---

<figure class="tva-flow">
  <figcaption class="tva-flow__caption">
    <span class="t-micro tva-flow__eyebrow">TVA · TRIGGER → VALUE → ASSET · STA GATE</span>
    <span class="t-h3 tva-flow__title">
      Every send passes through three components and a 7/9 scoring gate.
    </span>
  </figcaption>

  <!-- Layer 1: TVA structure -->
  <div class="tva-flow__structure" role="img" aria-label="TVA structure: Trigger flows to Value, Value flows to Asset. Each component has examples.">
    <div class="tva-flow__component">
      <div class="tva-flow__component-head">
        <span class="tva-flow__component-letter">T</span>
        <span class="tva-flow__component-name">Trigger</span>
      </div>
      <p class="tva-flow__component-desc">
        Observable, public event indicating active urgency. Last 30 days, ideally last 7.
      </p>
      <ul class="tva-flow__component-examples">
        <li>VP Sales hire posted</li>
        <li>Series B funded round</li>
        <li>Tech-stack change</li>
        <li>Regulatory filing</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <span class="tva-flow__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>

    <div class="tva-flow__component">
      <div class="tva-flow__component-head">
        <span class="tva-flow__component-letter">V</span>
        <span class="tva-flow__component-name">Value</span>
      </div>
      <p class="tva-flow__component-desc">
        The specific connection between the trigger and the prospect's active pain.
      </p>
      <ul class="tva-flow__component-examples">
        <li>"60-90 days from CRO search"</li>
        <li>"Engineering hire surge means..."</li>
        <li>"This filing predicts a buying window"</li>
        <li>Names the pain concretely</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <span class="tva-flow__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>

    <div class="tva-flow__component">
      <div class="tva-flow__component-head">
        <span class="tva-flow__component-letter">A</span>
        <span class="tva-flow__component-name">Asset</span>
      </div>
      <p class="tva-flow__component-desc">
        The artifact sent. Useful enough that the recipient would forward to their boss.
      </p>
      <ul class="tva-flow__component-examples">
        <li>90-day rebuild plan PDF</li>
        <li>Benchmark report</li>
        <li>Calculator or worksheet</li>
        <li>Specific peer-company comp</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Divider -->
  <div class="tva-flow__divider">
    <span class="t-micro tva-flow__divider-label">EVERY DRAFT THEN SCORES THROUGH</span>
    <span class="tva-flow__divider-arrow" aria-hidden="true">↓</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Layer 2: STA gate -->
  <div class="tva-flow__gate" role="img" aria-label="STA scoring gate: Specific 0-3, Timely 0-3, Actionable 0-3. Total 7+ sends. Below 7 regenerates. Three failed regenerations skip.">
    <div class="tva-flow__gate-head">
      <span class="t-micro tva-flow__gate-eyebrow">STA SCORING GATE · 0-3 PER CRITERION · PASS AT 7/9</span>
    </div>

    <div class="tva-flow__criteria">
      <div class="tva-flow__criterion">
        <div class="tva-flow__criterion-head">
          <span class="tva-flow__criterion-letter">S</span>
          <span class="tva-flow__criterion-name">Specific</span>
          <span class="t-micro tva-flow__criterion-range">0–3</span>
        </div>
        <p class="tva-flow__criterion-desc">Names. Numbers. Dates. Could it be sent to 50 others?</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tva-flow__criterion">
        <div class="tva-flow__criterion-head">
          <span class="tva-flow__criterion-letter">T</span>
          <span class="tva-flow__criterion-name">Timely</span>
          <span class="t-micro tva-flow__criterion-range">0–3</span>
        </div>
        <p class="tva-flow__criterion-desc">Last 30 days, ideally last 7.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tva-flow__criterion">
        <div class="tva-flow__criterion-head">
          <span class="tva-flow__criterion-letter">A</span>
          <span class="tva-flow__criterion-name">Actionable</span>
          <span class="t-micro tva-flow__criterion-range">0–3</span>
        </div>
        <p class="tva-flow__criterion-desc">Something they can do this week, not next quarter.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Decision flow -->
    <div class="tva-flow__decisions">
      <div class="tva-flow__decision tva-flow__decision--send">
        <span class="tva-flow__decision-tag">≥ 7 / 9</span>
        <span class="tva-flow__decision-action">SEND</span>
        <span class="t-micro tva-flow__decision-detail">+ forwardability check</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tva-flow__decision tva-flow__decision--regen">
        <span class="tva-flow__decision-tag">&lt; 7 / 9</span>
        <span class="tva-flow__decision-action">REGENERATE</span>
        <span class="t-micro tva-flow__decision-detail">try again with feedback</span>
      </div>
      <div class="tva-flow__decision tva-flow__decision--skip">
        <span class="tva-flow__decision-tag">3 FAILS</span>
        <span class="tva-flow__decision-action">SKIP</span>
        <span class="t-micro tva-flow__decision-detail">log and move on</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="t-micro tva-flow__footnote">
    Every subagent we ship reads <a href="/resources/tva-rubric/">tva-rubric.md</a> before deciding. Below 7/9, regenerate. Three failed regens, skip and log. The scoring is auditable per send.
  </p>
</figure>

<style>
  .tva-flow {
    margin: var(--space-12) 0;
    padding: var(--space-8);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--surface);
  }

  .tva-flow__caption {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .tva-flow__eyebrow { color: var(--muted); }
  .tva-flow__title { color: var(--ink); margin: 0; max-width: 600px; }

  /* Layer 1: TVA structure */
  .tva-flow__structure {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .tva-flow__component {
    padding: var(--space-5);
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .tva-flow__component-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-3);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .tva-flow__component-letter {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .tva-flow__component-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .tva-flow__component-desc {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .tva-flow__component-examples {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .tva-flow__component-examples li {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-micro);
    color: var(--muted);
    padding-left: var(--space-3);
    position: relative;
  }

  .tva-flow__component-examples li::before {
    content: '·';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .tva-flow__arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 24px;
  }

  /* Divider between layers */
  .tva-flow__divider {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    margin: var(--space-6) 0;
    padding: var(--space-4) 0;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--line);
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--line);
  }

  .tva-flow__divider-label { color: var(--muted); }

  .tva-flow__divider-arrow {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 20px;
  }

  /* Layer 2: STA gate */
  .tva-flow__gate {
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: var(--space-5);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-5);
  }

  .tva-flow__gate-head {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .tva-flow__gate-eyebrow { color: var(--muted); }

  .tva-flow__criteria {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .tva-flow__criterion {
    padding: var(--space-4);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    background: var(--surface);
  }

  .tva-flow__criterion-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .tva-flow__criterion-letter {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .tva-flow__criterion-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .tva-flow__criterion-range {
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-left: auto;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .tva-flow__criterion-desc {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .tva-flow__decisions {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding-top: var(--space-4);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .tva-flow__decision {
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 6px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-1);
    background: var(--surface);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .tva-flow__decision--send { border-color: var(--accent); }
  .tva-flow__decision--regen { border-color: var(--muted); }
  .tva-flow__decision--skip { border-color: var(--line); opacity: 0.85; }

  .tva-flow__decision-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--fs-micro);
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .tva-flow__decision-action {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .tva-flow__decision--send .tva-flow__decision-action { color: var(--accent); }
  .tva-flow__decision--regen .tva-flow__decision-action { color: var(--ink); }
  .tva-flow__decision--skip .tva-flow__decision-action { color: var(--muted); }

  .tva-flow__decision-detail {
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .tva-flow__footnote {
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .tva-flow__footnote a { color: var(--accent); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .tva-flow__structure { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .tva-flow__arrow { transform: rotate(90deg); padding: var(--space-2) 0; justify-self: center; }
    .tva-flow__criteria,
    .tva-flow__decisions { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
